    "Id": "chassisdef_black_knight_BL-IIC-KNT",
    "Name": "Black Knight IIC",
    "Details": "A typical IIC Version, the BL-IIC-KNT is rebuilt to be updated with Clan technology. Combining several types of weapons, its total weaponary is quite impressive considering its size. The largest weapon is its LBX AC/10, which is the only ballistic weapon except for two AMS for self-protection. The 'Mech carries three different type of missile launchers, one LRM-15, one SRM-6 and two Stream SRM-2. The remaining weapons are all energy based, one ER PPC and five lasers of various types. The heavy armament is only possible by using a 300 XL engine, Endo Steel chassis and Ferro-Fibrous armor. An Active Probe is mounted in the Center Torso.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>",
